acquireKitty(uint256,address).return: true if the acquisition was successful

becomeGhost(uint256).author: @ziweidream
becomeGhost(uint256).details: The kitty must be owned by the gameThis function can only be carried out via CronJobThis function will make a kitty permanently dead
becomeGhost(uint256).return: true if the kittie became a ghost and transferred to KittieHellDB

getKittyStatus(uint256).return: the previous kitty owner, the kitty dead status, the kitty playing status, the kitty ghost status, and the kitty death time
